 họ thề sẽ tìm ra kẻ bí ẩn muốn hãm hại chúng. Mặt khác, Triển Chiêu đã phát hiện ra manh mối. Triển Chiêu và Cẩm Mao Thử đều điều tra được hai người chết do sự cố cùng với vụ án 20 năm trước có liên qua đến nhau...</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"1030455","season":null,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2022-09-26T14:01:25.000Z","cast":["Ivan Xu","Leif Ye","Wang Yuwei","Li Shaoting","Yan Yanlong","Chen Xianmin","Lu Shun","Daniella Wang"],"director":["Ma Xiaolong"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Ivan Xu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ivan Xu","tmdb_id":3237531,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3JZuYwt7whUZPteu0Txn7Y1hqRJ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3237531"},{"name":"Leif Ye","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Leif Ye","tmdb_id":2482911,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1EzKOclfa3ox3LT8mq7jVbIpo17.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2482911"},{"name":"Wang Yuwei","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wang Yuwei","tmdb_id":3738434,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ylW9Ej90D8REGAzBMo0lOuhkSkx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3738434"},{"name":"Li Shaoting","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Li Shaoting","tmdb_id":3311178,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3311178"},{"name":"Yan Yanlong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yan Yanlong","tmdb_id":3913989,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3913989"},{"name":"Chen Xianmin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chen Xianmin","tmdb_id":3913982,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/da7oobGdPUJOazHP1kn3jE7HZWS.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3913982"},{"name":"Lu Shun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lu Shun","tmdb_id":4161695,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iWZ2wUUjMeEyRxFGzNswIqZGYj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4161695"},{"name":"Daniella Wang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Daniella Wang","tmdb_id":1320544,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4